data.description: SHORT SALE APPROVED PRICE - walk into your new home with over $40,000 in equity! Welcome to your 2021 home in the beautiful Timberlakes Community! Nestled in the trees on a huge corner lot! Enjoy a spacious & open floor plan, w/ 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, huge primary bedroom featuring walk in closet, shower & double vanity sinks. This well designed plan leaves plenty of room for entertaining w/ coffered 9ft ceilings, gorgeously upgraded kitchen w/island & all new appliances! All the parking for RV, Boat, cars & more. Timberlakes Community offers 5 parks, 2 stocked freshwater lakes w/ swimming docks & waterskiing, & private access boat launch to saltwater via Pickering Passage (harvest your own oysters & clams!) & a Community Clubhouse!
